# Roadmap for LLM Studio

## Phase 1: Core Development (Q1 - Q2 2024)
- Build foundational platform architecture.
- Integrate support for major blockchain networks.
- Develop initial automation and security modules.

## Phase 2: Beta Launch and Feedback (Q3 2024)
- Release public beta to early adopters.
- Collect user feedback and iterate on features.
- Launch analytics and dashboard components.

## Phase 3: Expansion & Security Audit (Q4 2024)
- Develop advanced automation workflows.
- Conduct comprehensive security audits.
- Expand community management tools.

## Phase 4: Official Launch and Partnerships (Q1 2025)
- Full platform launch.
- Initiate alliances with key web3 projects and integrations.
- Provide extensive documentation and support.

## Key Milestones
- Platform MVP completion
- Beta user onboarding
- Security certifications achieved
- Strategic partnership announcements

## Goals
- Short-term: Deliver a reliable beta and build an engaged user base.
- Long-term: Set the industry standard for web3 project automation tools.

## Future Expansion
- Incorporate AI-driven analytics.
- Support decentralized governance features.
- Extend multilingual and multi-chain support.